This paper deals with a multi-armed bandit problem with positive externalities, which is a subfield of machine learning and game theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Game Theory), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
